{"tid":579081,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"同總統踢波唔收腳    兩人賽後被捕","createTime":"2018-03-03T09:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T10:07:26.000Z","uid":60281,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef6e49a20a83a551b353ccb94144b30ad19a90b","tid":579081,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpxrRuFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpxrRuFE.jpg&h=6bd5a6f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕東非國家蒲隆地總統恩庫倫齊扎（Pierre Nkurunziza），帶著自己所組成的足球隊「Haleluya FC」在全國巡迴踢球，2月3日抵達北方城鎮基倫巴（Kiremba）時，當地球隊有眼不識泰山嚴加看管總統，甚至出現粗暴的肢體對抗，事後兩名主辦官員以謀逆總統罪被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據《BBC》報導，過去和恩庫倫齊扎踢球的球隊，通常都很清楚他們在與總統對陣，所以會放鬆防守好讓恩庫倫齊扎射門得分。然而，基倫巴足球隊裡有好幾名剛果難民，他們初來乍到根本不知道和他們比賽的是總統。<br />\n<br />\n恩庫倫齊扎因此吃盡苦頭，每次一控球就會被「好好招待」，而且還摔倒了好幾次。蒲隆地司法人士透露，基倫巴當地官員Cyriaque Nkezabahizi和他的助理Michel Mutama於3月1日雙雙被捕。"},{"pid":"f18da6c630ff976baf7dcc8a7f2222dbac0a40f0","tid":579081,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:19:18.000Z","msg":"韋亞嚟㗎？"},{"pid":"87c24d28d7608c5b37e3bb0749fbd400f6b21eb0","tid":579081,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:24:37.000Z","msg":"剷我波？用你個頭當波踢"},{"pid":"ba39f07667da62b51db898944c999abfa7c8e35b","tid":579081,"uid":158791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:07:26.000Z","msg":"趙穆"}]}